      "content": "You will find it in the acceptance of your own fragility, and the relinquishment of the need to control. The stillness that follows is not a destination, but a method of getting there – a surrender to the present, without expectation or hope. It is in the quiet abandonment of the self, that you may discover the space to begin anew.",
